article.description: — JaCobi Wood had 17 points as Belmont easily defeated Lipscomb 94-65 on Thursday night.
article.headline: Wood, Sheppard carry Belmont over Lipscomb 94-65
article.linkText: Wood, Sheppard carry Belmont over Lipscomb 94-65
article.story: NASHVILLE, Tenn. -- — JaCobi Wood had 17 points as Belmont easily defeated Lipscomb 94-65 on Thursday night. Ben Sheppard added 16 points for the Bruins, while Nick Muszynski chipped in 15 and blocked three shots. Luke Smith had 11 points for Belmont (6-3). Jacob Ognacevic had 20 points and eight rebounds for the Bisons (5-3). Parker Hazen added 15 points. Grant Asman distributed three assists. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/hub/college-basketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
